'''''Lwyll''''' was a modified [[Redthorn-class scout ship|''Redthorn''-class scout]] built and flown by the [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] [[Roa]] and named for his fiancée, [[Lwyll]]. It was lightly armed with three [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]], but was very fast and equipped with advanced [[Sensor/Legends|sensors]]. The [[Starship/Legends|ship]] sustained heavy damage during the [[Battle of Nar Shaddaa (4 BBY)|Battle of Nar Shaddaa]], and Roa was forced into crash landing on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. He was barely able to escape the ship before it exploded and was destroyed.

